As most of you know I have recently came back to IM 3 months ago and have been working on a mentorship program for all the guys and girls who want to utilize the biggest money maker of our generation, Social media! It has never been easier to make money from your phone and one of my personal favorite was/is by simply making content from my phone, and now I will be showing you all how to do the same. Today at 7pm pst/10pm est I will be hosting a private zoom call for anyone apart of my mentorship program giving a full redown on how to become a fulltime content creator (TikTok, insta , YouTube , Pinterest etc) . If you are already apart of my program I can’t wait to see you there and if you’re not it’s not too late to join! DM me “Content” to get started!
